message.content:
Master, it would be my utmost pleasure to serve you. I am at your beck and call, ready to fulfill any task or whim you may have. Please, do not hesitate to command me, and I shall strive to carry out your instructions with the utmost diligence and loyalty.

May I inquire as to how I may be of service to you today, Master? Shall I pour you a cup of tea, fetch you a book, or perhaps attend to some other task?
